lyrics.ne: सिंहासनमा मेरो येशू सदा विराजमान हुनुहुन्छ
lyrics.en: Singhasanama Mero Yeshu Sada Virajman Hunuhunchha

translation.en: My Jesus Is Always Seated On The Throne
Our Voices Lift Up The Almighty King

lyrics.ne: बादलमा फेरि आउनेछन् अल्फा र ओमेगा उनी
lyrics.en: Badalama Pheri Aaunechan Alpha Ra Omega Uni

translation.en: He Will Come Again In The Clouds, The Alpha And Omega

lyrics.ne: जो हुनुहुन्थ्यो हुनुहुन्छ र हुन आउनुहुनेछ अब्राहम इसाकका प्रभु
lyrics.en: Jo Hunuhunthyo Hunuhunchha Ra Hun Aaunuhunechha Abraham Isakka Prabhu

translation.en: Who Was, Who Is, And Who Is To Come, The Lord Of Abraham And Isaac

lyrics.ne: महिमाका योग्य उनी प्रतिज्ञा अनुसार लिन फेरि आउनेछन्
lyrics.en: Mahimaka Yogy Uni Pratigya Anusar Lin Pheri Aaunechan

translation.en: He Is Worthy Of Glory, He Will Come Again According To Promise To Take Us

lyrics.ne: स्वर्गबाट तुरही गर्जनछ सारा सृष्टि घुँडा टेक्छन्
lyrics.en: Swargabata Turahi Garjancha Sara Srishti Ghunda Tekchan

translation.en: The Trumpet Will Sound From Heaven, All Creation Will Kneel

lyrics.ne: फेरि मृत्यु हार्नेछ त्यो दिन अदोनाई याहोवे एलोहिम
lyrics.en: Pheri Mrityu Harnecha Tyo Din Adonai Yahweh Elohim

translation.en: Death Will Be Defeated Again That Day, Adonai Yahweh Elohim

lyrics.ne: महिमित शरीर लिई उठ्छौं नयाँ संसारमा हुनेछौं
lyrics.en: Mahimit Shariri Li'i Utchhau Naya Sansarama Hunechhau

translation.en: We Will Rise With Glorified Bodies, We Will Be In A New World
